<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-166] Document new &quot;lctl set_param -P&quot; option</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-166</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The new &quot;lctl set_param -P&quot; syntax for setting permanent configuration parameters in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3155&quot; title=&quot;Permanent parameters with lctl set_param -P&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3155&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3155&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; needs to be added to the Lustre manual.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="19744">LUDOC-166</key>
            <summary>Document new &quot;lctl set_param -P&quot; option</summary>
