                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="72584" author="jlevi" created="Mon, 2 Dec 2013 14:10:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch has landed to update Lustre Manual.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="72572" author="artem_blagodarenko" created="Mon, 2 Dec 2013 12:32:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Change has been successfully cherry-picked as e7c70e91537ec213122dfed94966eb53c228ae7a&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch is merged. Can we close this issue?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="65144" author="artem_blagodarenko" created="Tue, 27 Aug 2013 10:11:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/7458&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/7458&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="64817" author="artem_blagodarenko" created="Thu, 22 Aug 2013 08:45:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andreas, I will do it before this weekends.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="64617" author="adilger" created="Tue, 20 Aug 2013 16:13:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Artem, when are you planning to submit an update to the Lustre User Manual for this feature?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="62051" author="adilger" created="Wed, 10 Jul 2013 20:53:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Directions for contributing to the manual:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Making+changes+to+the+Lustre+Manual&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Making+changes+to+the+Lustre+Manual&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think the Lustre manual update should be done in two stages:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add a new section describing &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl set_param -P&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; in parallel with the existing &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl conf_param&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; documentation.  This new section should be marked and described with the &quot;new in 2.5&quot; tags like &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;para condition=&apos;l25&apos;&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;At some future date, remove mention of the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl conf_param&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; option from the manual.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
